#. 1: raw
msgctxt "EnemyBokoblin_00"
msgid ""
"Bokoblins<1.ra>Without much in the way of clothing to protect them, they "
"tend to\n"
"run when menaced by bees."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "EnemyBokoblin_01"
msgid ""
"Bokoblins<1.ra>These omnivorous monsters enjoy not only meat and fish but"
" also\n"
"fresh fruit."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "EnemyChuchu_00"
msgid ""
"Chuchus<1.ra>They will explode when attacked. Try throwing something at "
"them\n"
"from a safe distance."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "EnemyGuardian_00"
msgid ""
"Guardians<1.ra>Guardians are ancient, highly advanced weapons, so items "
"from the\n"
"current age won't deal much damage. Weapons from their own era\n"
"like ancient arrows are better suited to combat them."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "EnemyLizalfos_00"
msgid "Lizalfos<1.ra>As carnivores, they eat meat, fish, and even insects."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "EnemyMoriblin_00"
msgid ""
"Moblins<1.ra>These large carnivores require sizable helpings of meat and "
"fish\n"
"to sustain their bulky frames."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Tactics_00"
msgid ""
"Stealth Tip<1.ra>It's harder to hear footsteps when it's raining...making"
" it the\n"
"perfect time to sneak up on some monsters!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Tactics_01"
msgid ""
"Stealth Tip<1.ra>Crouching in a grassy field makes it harder for monsters"
" and enemies\n"
"to detect you. Keep this in mind if you want to ambush enemies or\n"
"avoid fighting altogether."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Tactics_02"
msgid ""
"Critical Hits<1.ra>Hitting a monster or enemy in the head with an arrow "
"deals double\n"
"the normal amount of damage."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Tactics_03"
msgid ""
"Horseback Battles<1.ra>When fighting on horseback, weapons with reach "
"such as spears and\n"
"big swords have an advantage over short swords and clubs."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Tactics_04"
msgid ""
"Battle Tip<1.ra>The difference between winning and losing a battle often "
"comes down\n"
"to strategy. With the right tactics, you may be able to defeat an entire\n"
"group of enemies at once."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Tactics_05"
msgid ""
"Battle Tip<1.ra>Monsters sometimes leave their weapons lying around their"
" camp.\n"
"Sneaking up and stealing these items will make defeating them\n"
"much easier!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Tactics_06"
msgid ""
"Ice Arrows<1.ra>If you find yourself surrounded by an overwhelming number"
" of\n"
"enemies, try using ice arrows to freeze them in their tracks."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Tactics_07"
msgid ""
"Fire Arrows<1.ra>Use fire arrows to burn dry grass and defeat multiple "
"enemies\n"
"at the same time."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Tactics_08"
msgid ""
"Shock Arrows<1.ra>Shoot shock arrows into water or metallic objects to "
"electrify\n"
"enemies and monsters."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Tactics_09"
msgid ""
"Battle Tip<1.ra>Monsters on the lookout in watchtowers will sound the "
"alarm if they\n"
"spot you. Defeat these foes first before they alert the others."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Tactics_10"
msgid ""
"Battle Tip<1.ra>If an enemy camp has multiple levels, each packed with "
"monsters,\n"
"consider using the paraglider to sneak your way to the top."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Tactics_11"
msgid ""
"Battle Tip<1.ra>Using Magnesis to toss metal objects into a camp full of "
"monsters\n"
"is a great way to do some damage."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
#. 2: icon
msgctxt "Tactics_12"
msgid ""
"Battle Tip<1.ra>Monsters have a harder time detecting you if you press "
"<2.ic>\n"
"to crouch and quietly approach them."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Tactics_13"
msgid ""
"Battle Tip<1.ra>Monsters need their beauty rest too. If you see a group "
"of monsters\n"
"sleeping, use that opportunity to sneak-attack them!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Tactics_14"
msgid ""
"Bomb Barrels<1.ra>Shoot a fire arrow into a bomb barrel to make it "
"explode.\n"
"Tossing a burning weapon at one works too."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Tactics_15"
msgid ""
"Electric Chuchus<1.ra>When you attack Electric Chuchus, they explode in a"
" burst of sparks.\n"
"Use this to your advantage to shock nearby monsters."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Tactics_16"
msgid ""
"Fire Chuchus<1.ra>When you attack Fire Chuchus, they explode and start a "
"fire.\n"
"Use this to your advantage to turn up the heat on nearby monsters."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Tactics_17"
msgid ""
"Ice Chuchus<1.ra>When you attack Ice Chuchus, they explode in a burst of "
"frost.\n"
"Use this to your advantage to put nearby monsters on ice."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Tactics_18"
msgid ""
"Critical Hits<1.ra>Weapons that you have no use for are perfect for "
"throwing\n"
"at monsters. If one hits, it will deal double damage."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Tactics_19"
msgid ""
"Battle Tip<1.ra>If the foe you're fighting is too powerful, train "
"yourself up! You can\n"
"start by finding a stronger weapon or collecting Spirit Orbs\n"
"to get more hearts or increase your Stamina Wheel."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Tactics_20"
msgid ""
"Electric Lizalfos<1.ra>If you hit an Electric Lizalfos's horn with an "
"arrow, it will discharge\n"
"a massive electric shock."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
#. 2: icon
msgctxt "Tactics_21"
msgid ""
"Horseback Battles<1.ra>When fighting on horseback, use <2.ic> to focus "
"your attention,\n"
"making it easier to aim."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Tactics_22"
msgid ""
"Battle Tip<1.ra>If a monster is hiding behind a shield, you can bat the "
"shield away\n"
"by hitting it with a heavy sword or axe."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Tactics_23"
msgid ""
"Elemental Weaknesses<1.ra>If you use a fiery attack against an icy enemy,"
" you may defeat it\n"
"in one hit."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Tactics_24"
msgid ""
"Elemental Weaknesses<1.ra>If you use an icy attack against a fiery enemy,"
" you may defeat it\n"
"in one hit."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
msgctxt "Tactics_25"
msgid ""
"Perfect Dodge<1.ra>If you backflip or side hop away from a monster's "
"attack at just the\n"
"right moment, you will be rewarded with a chance to let loose\n"
"with a flurry of attacks."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
#. 2: icon
msgctxt "Tactics_26"
msgid ""
"Perfect Guard<1.ra>When equipped with a shield, if you press <2.ic> to "
"deflect a monster's\n"
"attack at just the right moment, you will be rewarded with a chance to\n"
"counter the attack."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
#. 2: icon
msgctxt "Tactics_27"
msgid ""
"Charged Attack<1.ra>You can ready a charged attack by holding <2.ic>. "
"Doing so depletes\n"
"your stamina, so be sure to time your attack carefully."
msgstr ""

#. 1: raw
#. 2: icon
msgctxt "Tactics_28"
msgid ""
"Jump Slash<1.ra>Perform a jump slash by pressing <2.ic> after jumping or "
"while in the\n"
"air. The shock wave created when you hit the ground can affect\n"
"nearby monsters."
msgstr ""

